  <name>Mockoon</name>
  <summary>Create mock APIs in seconds</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Mockoon is the easiest and quickest way to run mock APIs locally.
      No remote deployment, no account required, open source.
    </p>
    <p>
      Features include:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Unlimited number of mock local servers and routes</li>
      <li>Complete control over server responses</li>
      <li>Use templating for dynamic responses</li>
      <li>Record and auto-mock HTTP traffic</li>
      <li>Proxy mode to forward non-matching requests</li>
      <li>Support for HTTPS, CORS, and more</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  <developer_name>Mockoon</developer_name>

